“When you can market well, that’s a win but when you are who you say you are, you gon win universally and you’re going to win in terms of longevity.” -Derrick Grace II 

Derrick Grace II (@derrickgracetwo) has Manifested Millions By Being Himself Unapologetically 

After becoming unemployed from a good paying job he knew something had to change.  Surprisingly his decision consisted of him becoming permanently unemployable while attacking stigmas. 

Fast forward to today, he’s now a serial entrepreneur, a best-selling author, educator and a full-time father working to build empires. 

Derrick Grace II is a billionaire in the making
